crime_fact:
Crime Facts
The defendant was sentenced to 1 year in prison and 2 years of suspended execution by the Incheon District Court, Bucheon Branch, on April 24, 2015, for fraud, etc., and the judgment became final on May 2, 2015.
The defendant is a domestic cash withdrawal agent connected to a so-called phishing fraud organization linked with Chinese individuals.
In conspiracy with unidentified members of the phishing organization (alias 'D'), the defendant used fake websites and internet access programs of domestic financial institutions created by the phishing organization members through unknown methods to obtain victims' financial information. Then, by transferring the victims' money to a predetermined account, the defendant, possessing the check card linked to the account where the money was transferred, was instructed by 'D' to withdraw the money in cash and transfer it to another predetermined account.
An unidentified member of the phishing organization spread malware capable of accessing fake financial institution websites, creating personal information input fields related to financial fraud, and acquiring the financial information entered by victims, through unknown methods in an unspecified location in China around 2014. This malware infected a computer installed at the office of Company G, located in Seobuk-gu, Cheonan-si, Chungcheongnam-do, with victim F as its representative.
On September 24, 2014, around 17:18, the company's accountant H, unaware of the malware infection on the office computer, accessed the KB Kookmin Bank internet banking site using the computer. A popup window appeared, unusually prompting to register for a "Financial Information Leakage Secondary Damage Prevention Service." Believing it to be a normal procedure of the financial institution, H entered the financial information of Company G, including the Kookmin Bank account number, account password, transfer password, and digital certificate password, and similarly entered the financial information of the company's NH Bank account.
Using the financial information of Company G entered by H, who was deceived by the fake site on September 24, 2014, around 17:18, the unidentified member of the phishing organization transferred 268,000,000 won stored in Company G's Kookmin Bank account (account number I) and NH Bank account (account number J) into 13,000,000 won to a Saemaul Geumgo account under the name of K (account number L), 30,000,000 won to a Shinhan Bank account under the name of M (account number N), another 30,000,000 won to a different Shinhan Bank account under the name of M (account number O), 30,000,000 won to a Post Office account under the name of P (account number Q), and continued on September 25, 2014, around 08:40, transferring 30,000,000 won to a Hana Daetoo Securities account under the name of R (account number S), 20,000,000 won to a Hana Daetoo Securities account under the name of T (account number U), 20,000,000 won to a Dongyang Securities account under the name of T (account number V), 10,000,000 won to a Dongbu Securities account under the name of T (account number W), 20,000,000 won to an IBK account under the name of X (account number Y), 20,000,000 won to a Shinhyup account under the name of Z (account number AA), 20,000,000 won to an IBK account under the name of AB (account number AC), and 25,000,000 won to a Kookmin Bank account under the name of AD (account number AE).
Subsequently, the defendant, using the check card of the Shinhan Bank account under the name of M, which he had in possession, withdrew a total of 25,564,600 won from around September 24 to 25, 2014, and transferred it to a person or account as instructed by 'D'.
Thus, the defendant facilitated the acquisition of a property benefit amounting to 25,564,600 won by aiding 'D' and others in unauthorizedly entering and altering information in computers and other information processing devices, thereby facilitating their information processing.

target_node.label: C_10
target_node.text: It can be clearly proven that the defendant had the intent to aid and abet the fraudulent act.

target_reason: Claim c00010 argues that the defendant's direct involvement in the bidding process is not persuasive, but this is merely an inference based on a fundamental understanding of the defendant's role and criminal act. This claim does not present concrete evidence or data that clearly proves the defendant's direct involvement, but is based solely on the fact that they were involved in the development and installation of malicious software. Therefore, this claim tends to exaggerate or definitively conclude the defendant's role in the bidding process, including a logical leap.

nodes.label: MC_01
nodes.text: The defendant was unaware of the fact that they had obtained financial benefits from the fraudulent act. Therefore, due to the lack of intent, they cannot be considered an accomplice to the crime of fraud.

nodes.label: MC_01
nodes.text: The defendant has a prior conviction for a similar fraud offense and facilitated the fraud by continuously communicating with a co-conspirator during the commission of the crime. This suggests that the defendant was aware of the essential elements of the fraud offense, clearly indicating intent.

nodes.label: C_01
nodes.text: The defendant did not recognize the essential elements of the crime.

nodes.label: W_01
nodes.text: If there is no intent to commit a crime, the act cannot be considered as aiding and abetting the crime.

nodes.label: D_01
nodes.text: The defendant merely withdrew or transferred money following the instructions of 'D', and was not aware of the fact that these actions themselves resulted in obtaining financial benefits from the fraud.

nodes.label: C_02
nodes.text: The defendant was unaware of the details of the criminal plan.

nodes.label: W_02
nodes.text: If the defendant was unaware of the details of the criminal plan, he cannot have the intentionality of the crime, and this can mitigate his responsibility.

nodes.label: D_02
nodes.text: The defendant is accused of conspiring with members of a phishing organization, including an unidentified person (alias 'D'), to obtain financial information and transfer the victim's money. However, it is claimed that they were unaware of the specific plans or the methods used to acquire the victims' financial information.

nodes.label: C_03
nodes.text: The defendant only played the role of an accomplice and was not specifically aware of the principal offender's plan or method of execution.

nodes.label: W_03
nodes.text: If the accomplice was not specifically aware of the principal offender's plan or method of execution, his actions lack intent, and this can be an important factor in mitigating criminal liability.

nodes.label: D_03
nodes.text: The defendant only received withdrawal instructions from 'D' and was unaware of how an unidentified member of the phishing organization discovered the victim's financial information using fake financial institution websites and computer internet access programs, nor did they know the specific plans or methods used to transfer the victim's funds.

nodes.label: C_04
nodes.text: The defendant actively participated in the fraud by maintaining continuous contact with the co-conspirator.

nodes.label: W_04
nodes.text: Continuous contact and cooperation with a co-conspirator is clear evidence of criminal conspiracy, which means that the defendant actively participated in and conspired in the crime.

nodes.label: D_04
nodes.text: The defendant agreed to withdraw the said funds in cash upon receiving withdrawal instructions from 'D' and to transfer them to a predetermined account.

nodes.label: C_05
nodes.text: The defendant has a prior conviction for a similar crime, which suggests that the defendant fully understood the nature of the crime.

nodes.label: W_05
nodes.text: Having a previous conviction indicates an awareness and understanding of the crime, which strongly suggests the presence of intent.

nodes.label: D_05
nodes.text: The defendant was sentenced to 1 year in prison and 2 years of suspended sentence for fraud and other charges at the Bucheon branch of the Incheon District Court on April 24, 2015. This judgment was finalized on May 2, 2015.

nodes.label: C_06
nodes.text: The defendant collaborated with a phishing scam organization to commit crimes using the victim's financial information.

nodes.label: W_06
nodes.text: Discovering the victim's financial information and using it to transfer funds requires a high degree of planning and organized conspiracy, and the defendant's actions played a significant role in the execution of the fraud.

nodes.label: D_06
nodes.text: The defendant, in conspiracy with members of a phishing organization including an unidentified person (alias 'D'), used fake websites of domestic financial institutions and internet access programs on computers, which were created by the phishing organization members through unknown methods, to obtain victims' financial information. Subsequently, they arbitrarily transferred the victims' money to pre-determined accounts.

nodes.label: C_07
nodes.text: The defendant lacked intent as they were unaware of the details of the phishing scam organization's activities.

nodes.label: W_07
nodes.text: The fact that the defendant merely withdrew or transferred money following 'D's instructions does not mean that the defendant was aware of the entire scheme or details of the phishing scam.

nodes.label: D_07
nodes.text: The defendant conspired with members of a phishing organization, including an unidentified person known as 'D', to use fake websites of domestic financial institutions and computer internet access programs created by the phishing organization members through unknown methods to obtain victims' financial information. After obtaining this information, they arbitrarily transferred the victims' money to a predetermined account. The defendant, possessing the check card linked to the account where the money was transferred, agreed to withdraw the money in cash upon receiving instructions from 'D' and then transfer it to another predetermined account.

nodes.label: C_08
nodes.text: Even if the defendant has a previous conviction for fraud, it cannot be conclusively determined that there was intent in this case.

nodes.label: W_08
nodes.text: A past guilty verdict does not necessarily mean that the defendant was aware of the specific nature and detailed method of the fraudulent act in this case.

nodes.label: D_08
nodes.text: The defendant was sentenced to 1 year in prison and 2 years of suspended sentence for fraud and other charges at the Bucheon branch of the Incheon District Court on April 24, 2015. This judgment was finalized on May 2, 2015.

nodes.label: C_09
nodes.text: The defendant cannot be considered an accomplice to the crime of fraud since they did not directly obtain or use the victim's financial information.

nodes.label: W_09
nodes.text: To be recognized as an accomplice to the crime of fraud, there must be an act that directly aids in the execution of the crime, and the defendant is merely performing the role of withdrawing or transferring money as instructed.

nodes.label: D_09
nodes.text: An unidentified member of a phishing organization, in an unspecified date in 2014, in an unknown location in China, distributed malware capable of accessing fake financial institution websites, creating input fields for financial fraud-related personal information, and acquiring financial information entered by victims through an unknown method. This malware infected a computer installed in the office of Company G, represented by victim F, located in Seobuk-gu, Cheonan-si, Chungcheongnam-do.

nodes.label: C_10
nodes.text: It can be clearly proven that the defendant had the intent to aid and abet the fraudulent act.

nodes.label: W_10
nodes.text: The fact that the defendant continuously communicated with 'D' and proceeded with cash withdrawals and transfers shows a clear intent to aid and abet the fraud.

nodes.label: D_10
nodes.text: The defendant, using a Shinhan Bank check card for an account held under the name M, which they had in their possession beforehand, withdrew a total of 25,564,600 won from around September 24, 2014, to September 25, 2014, and transferred it to a person directed by 'D' or into an account as instructed by 'D'.

nodes.label: C_11
nodes.text: The defendant was fully aware of the essential elements of the fraud offense.

nodes.label: W_11
nodes.text: The involvement of a defendant, who has already been convicted of a similar type of crime, in the same type of criminal activity again suggests that there was sufficient awareness of the essential elements of the crime and deliberate action utilizing that knowledge.

nodes.label: D_11
nodes.text: The defendant was sentenced to 1 year in prison and 2 years of suspended sentence for fraud and other charges at the Bucheon branch of the Incheon District Court on April 24, 2015. This judgment was finalized on May 2, 2015.

nodes.label: C_12
nodes.text: The defendant cannot substantiate the claim that they simply acted as instructed.

nodes.label: W_12
nodes.text: The conspiracy relationship between the defendant and the members of the phishing organization, as well as the specific roles played, show that the defendant went beyond being a mere executor of orders and directly aided in the commission of the crime.

nodes.label: D_12
nodes.text: The defendant conspired with members of a phishing organization, including an unidentified person known as 'D', to use fake websites of domestic financial institutions and computer internet access programs created by the phishing organization members through unknown methods to obtain victims' financial information. After obtaining this information, they would arbitrarily transfer the victims' money to a predetermined account. The defendant, possessing the check card linked to the account where the money was transferred, would then receive withdrawal instructions from 'D' and withdraw the money in cash to transfer it to another predetermined account.

nodes.label: C_13
nodes.text: The defendant was fully aware of the essential elements of the fraud crime.

nodes.label: W_13
nodes.text: Given that the defendant has previously been sentenced to imprisonment for fraud and was on probation, it is understood that they would have had awareness and understanding of the fraud crime.

nodes.label: D_13
nodes.text: The defendant was sentenced to 1 year in prison and 2 years of suspended sentence for fraud and other charges at the Bucheon branch of the Incheon District Court on April 24, 2015. This judgment was finalized on May 2, 2015.

nodes.label: C_14
nodes.text: The defendant abetted the fraud, which demonstrates that there was an intent to abet.

nodes.label: W_14
nodes.text: The fact that the defendant received direct withdrawal instructions from 'D' and withdrew and transferred the funds demonstrates that this act played a significant role in the execution of the fraud.

nodes.label: D_14
nodes.text: Subsequently, the defendant used a Shinhan Bank check card, which belonged to M and was in the defendant's possession beforehand, to withdraw a total of 25,564,600 won from around September 24, 2014, to September 25, 2014. The defendant then delivered the money to a person directed by 'D' or transferred it to an account as instructed by 'D'.

nodes.label: C_15
nodes.text: Despite being fully aware of the criminal act through a previous conviction, the defendant repeated the same type of criminal behavior.

nodes.label: W_15
nodes.text: Despite having awareness and experience of fraud crimes due to a previous conviction, repeating the same type of crime demonstrates clear intent.

nodes.label: D_15
nodes.text: The defendant was sentenced to 1 year in prison and 2 years of suspended sentence for fraud, etc., by the Bucheon branch of the Incheon District Court on April 24, 2015, and the judgment became final on May 2, 2015.

nodes.label: C_16
nodes.text: There is insufficient evidence that the defendant intentionally participated in the fraud crime.

nodes.label: W_16
nodes.text: Just because the defendant was found guilty in the past does not mean that they acted with the same awareness and intent in this case.

nodes.label: D_16
nodes.text: The defendant claimed not to have known that the money was obtained through fraud, stating that they merely withdrew or transferred the money following orders.

nodes.label: C_17
nodes.text: The fact that the defendant was unaware of the essential elements of the crime must be considered in the legal judgment.

nodes.label: W_17
nodes.text: It is difficult to acknowledge intent without an understanding of the essential elements of a crime.

nodes.label: D_17
nodes.text: The defendant is emphasizing that they were unaware the money was obtained through fraudulent activities.

nodes.label: C_18
nodes.text: The defendant's actions lack intent, thus cannot be seen as an accomplice to the crime of fraud.

nodes.label: W_18
nodes.text: In the absence of intent, one cannot be considered an accomplice to a crime.

nodes.label: D_18
nodes.text: The defendant merely withdrew or transferred money upon instruction, and cannot be considered to have recognized the essential elements of the crime.
